e alleged bearer of ill fortune. This POK\u00e9MON shows strong interest in anything that sparkles or glitters. It will even try to steal rings from women."},{"version":"emerald","text":"MURKROW were feared as the alleged bearers of ill fortune. It shows strong interest in anything that sparkles. It will even try to steal rings from women."},{"version":"firered","text":"It is said that when chased, it lures its attacker onto dark mountain trails where the foe will get lost."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Feared and loathed by many, it is believed to bring misfortune to all those who see it at night."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It is believed that seeing this Pok\u00e9mon at night will bring about ominous occurrences."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It appears near travelers to lure them into deep forests. It is said to carry misfortune."},{"version":"platinum","text":"If spotted, it will lure an unwary person into chasing it, then lose the pursuer on mountain trails."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Feared and loathed by many, it is believed to bring misfortune to all those who see it at night."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It is said that when chased, it lures its attacker onto dark mountain trails where the foe will get lost."},{"version":"black","text":"If spotted, it will lure an unwary person into chasing it, then lose the pursuer on mountain trails."},{"version":"white","text":"If spotted, it will lure an unwary person into chasing it, then lose the pursuer on mountain trails."},{"version":"black-2","text":"If spotted, it will lure an unwary person into chasing it then lose the pursuer on mountain trails."},{"version":"white-2","text":"If spotted, it will lure an unwary person into chasing it then lose the pursuer on mountain trails."},{"version":"x","text":"It hides any shiny object it finds in a secret location. Murkrow and Meowth loot one another\u2019s stashes."},{"version":"y","text":"Feared and loathed by many, it is believed to bring misfortune to